{"tid":981180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【民族黨禁運作】陳浩天出席上訴聆訊","createTime":"2019-01-14T05:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T14:09:52.000Z","uid":47359,"like":52,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b576f90a4db72ba1d704646c01e2719c4b46e251","tid":981180,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190114/s00001/1547431205386/%e3%80%90%e6%b0%91%e6%97%8f%e9%bb%a8%e7%a6%81%e9%81%8b%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%91%e9%99%b3%e6%b5%a9%e5%a4%a9%e5%87%ba%e5%b8%ad%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%e8%81%86%e8%a8%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190114%2Fs00001%2F1547431205386%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%2597%258f%25e9%25bb%25a8%25e7%25a6%2581%25e9%2581%258b%25e4%25bd%259c%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%2599%25b3%25e6%25b5%25a9%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%25b8%25ad%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4%25e8%2581%2586%25e8%25a8%258a&d=v0UtrIthVh3L%2FppYQHlmQttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c06b4a1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190114%2Fs00001%2F1547431205386%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25b0%2591%25e6%2597%258f%25e9%25bb%25a8%25e7%25a6%2581%25e9%2581%258b%25e4%25bd%259c%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%2599%25b3%25e6%25b5%25a9%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%25b8%25ad%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4%25e8%2581%2586%25e8%25a8%258a&h=43253220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190114/s00001/1547431205386/%e3%80%90%e6%b0%91%e6%97%8f%e9%bb%a8%e7%a6%81%e9%81%8b%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%91%e9%99%b3%e6%b5%a9%e5%a4%a9%e5%87%ba%e5%b8%ad%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%e8%81%86%e8%a8%8a</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局引用《社團條例》禁香港民族黨運作，香港民族黨前召集人陳浩天隨後提出上訴。處理上訴的行政會議今早舉行，拿着大疊文件的陳浩天親自出席聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天早前要求8名行會成員避席，包括保安局長李家超、教育局長楊潤雄、行會召集人陳智思、資深大律師湯家驊，以及立法會議員葉劉淑儀、黃國健、劉業強、張國鈞。據了解，大部分被點名的成員，都被行會秘書處通知要避席。<br />\n<br />\n保安局去年引用《社團條例》作出命令，禁止香港民族黨在香港運作或繼續運作，是回歸以來首次有政黨在《社團條例》下被禁止運作。"},{"pid":"a75be39f37cddef9244eb355a24bd6e90e793323","tid":981180,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b37e4e3198b7553cf275e27d04419e36dc2584","tid":981180,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"2d84c75eeee7fa848c2c9a88f19416837f7748a3","tid":981180,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:21:10.000Z","msg":"佢親自出席算唔算「以非法社團成員身分行事」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95f3192a9f66446d3bd235501b9c578ca830abc","tid":981180,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"16a74e16bd2bc6e6f5b566ebdd0599843daf68cd","tid":981180,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1fc54ff5b0847e95f7bdd4f2c4ce780be1974874","tid":981180,"uid":73420,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"聲名黨"},{"pid":"af236f4be0dcc80acb681749cf0a1076bf148c2c","tid":981180,"uid":47359,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"1fc54ff5b0847e95f7bdd4f2c4ce780be1974874","tid":981180,"uid":73420,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"聲名黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"聲明到中國驚到要取締"},{"pid":"20717ff2b5ee07def03a1b4c1dc12f37f3b2c3cc","tid":981180,"uid":175623,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"邊撚個話獨派冇做野去食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70205e87128bbc63c5e1a4080b51c6cdb5f2eeb","tid":981180,"uid":47359,"